videos.headline: Auburn throws interception, Ole Miss' Hugh Freeze celebrates with The Whip
videos.description: Auburn QB Sean White throws the ball up into double coverage and Ole Miss' Tony Bridges comes down with the interception.

videos.headline: S. White pass,to R. Louis for 47 yds for a TD
videos.description: Sean White pass complete to Ricardo Louis for 47 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Ole Miss RB fools two defenders on 25-yard TD
videos.description: Ole Miss RB Akeem Judd makes two defenders miss and scampers into the end zone for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Auburn's Countess won't be denied interception
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Chad Kelly's pass is broken up, and Auburn's Blake Countess comes down with the ball after tipping it to himself.

videos.headline: S. White pass,to M. Ray for 44 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Sean White pass complete to Melvin Ray for 44 yds to the Miss 37 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Chad Kelly connects with Derrick Jones to break tie
videos.description: Chad Kelly throws to Derrick Jones, who shakes off two defenders to get in for the 45-yard touchdown to give Ole Miss the lead.

videos.headline: S. White pass,to R. Louis for 46 yds for a 1ST down

videos.headline: C. Kelly pass intercepted,K. Frost return  for 0 yds

videos.headline: Auburn reaches into bag of tricks for long gain
videos.description: Auburn's offense gives the ball to a few players before Jeremy Johnson throws downfield to Tony Stevens for the 45-yard gain.

videos.headline: Treadwell's incredible catch secures TD for Ole Miss
videos.description: Chad Kelly throws to Laquon Treadwell, who makes a great over-the-shoulder catch for the 21-yard touchdown.
